        </item>
        <item>
         <widget class="QComboBox" name="surfaceTechniqueComboBox">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Isosurface mesh (marching cubes) builds a solid shaded brain surface at the threshold - low perfusion falls inward as crisp dents (recommended, closest to the Amen look). Volume render is the GPU ray-cast for comparison.</string>
