         </widget>
        </item>
        <item>
         <widget class="QComboBox" name="surfaceColorSchemeComboBox">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Amen spectrum: a positional rainbow (pink superior -&gt; violet inferior) like the real Amen surface, with lighting carrying the shape. Solid sculpt: one matte tissue tone. Hole-emphasis / Perfusion rainbow: tint the surface by underlying uptake. Color applies to either technique.</string>
